ub><italic>i,j</italic></sub> are the timings of incoming spikes. Somatic spiking is given by an Integrate and fire model with adaptation<sup><xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR66">66</xref></sup>:<disp-formula id="Equ2"><label>2</label><alternatives><tex-math id="M3">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
